;TODO: ENT_022 = ♫ +500 Blind: Gain a lead of more than 500 points, but without seeing the notes!
;TODO: ENT_023 = ♫ Blind 2000/5000/7000: Race to 2000/5000/7000 points, but without seeing the notes!
;TODO: ENT_024 = ♫ Blind Mode: A 1v1 duel, but with the notes hidden!
;TODO: ENT_025 = ♫ Deaf: Think you know the notes? Can you sing it without the accompaniment?
;TODO: ENT_026 = ♫ Duel: A 1v1 duel to get the highest score!
;TODO: ENT_027 = ♫ Hardcore: Battle for a three-line lead on your opponent!
;TODO: ENT_028 = ♫ Hold the Blind: Keep your rating above the line for the longest, but with the notes hidden!
;TODO: ENT_028 = ♫ Hold the Line: Keep your rating above the line for the longest!
;TODO: ENT_029 = ♫ No Lyrics: Think you know all the lyrics? Sing with the lyrics hidden!
;TODO: ENT_030 = ♫ Short Song: A fast-paced 1v1 duel over half the song!
;TODO: ENT_031 = ♫ Total Darkness!: A duel, but with the notes and the lyrics hidden. Only for the brave!
;TODO: ENT_032 = ♫ Until 2000/5000/7000: Race to 2000/5000/7000 Points!
